item.description: The shirts have been ordered and I will be printing and pressing them this week. If anyone did not order one and would like one, please contact me at blacklab08022@comcast.net. You can look at the past meetups to see the details. I was thinking maybe we can meet up in the parking lot at Livingston Park in Manchester on Tuesday, June 26th at 6 pm. If this doesn't work, I can also meetup on Wed. the 27th or Thurs. the 28th. How does everyone feel about that? I will set it for the 26th, but will work with whomever can't make that date.
